<h2 style="text-align: left;">Once Upon A Bride There Was A Forest</h2>
<h6>by Kristen Palmer</h6>
<h6>directed by<strong> Heather Cohn
</strong></h6>
<h6>Dec 6 to Dec 20, 2014</h6>
<p style="padding-left: 5px;"><span style="color: #ffffff;">--</span>
The 4th Street Theatre
83 East 4th street
New York, NY
<a href="https://goo.gl/maps/D1bO5" target="_blank">map</a></p>

