[one_fourth]
<h5>Rachael Hip-Flores (Josie)</h5>
WITH FLUX: <em>Sans Merci</em>, <em>Hearts Like Fists</em>, <em>DEINDE</em>. SELECTED NY THEATRE: <em>Faust</em> (God), <em>Cymbeline</em> (Imogen), <em>Trying</em> (Lena, World Premiere), readings at the Public and Cherry Lane Theaters, and with Harvey Fierstein, Kristen Johnston, Lee Tergesen, and Reed Birney. SELECTED WEBSERIES: <em>Anyone But Me</em> (Winner, Best Lead Actress: IAWTV, Streamy, Indie Soap Awards), <em>Producing Juliet</em> (Nominated: Best Lead/Supporting Actress – Rome Web Awards, Indie Series Awards, Best Ensemble – Indie Series Awards) SELECTED FILM/TV: <em>Gossip Girl</em>.
