[one_fourth_last]
<h5>Brian Silliman (Man)</h5>
Recent credits include <em>The Pumpkin Pie Show: Seasick, Over, Dark Water</em> (NY IT Nomination for Best Lead Actor), <em>Kill Shakespeare, Breaking Kayfabe, The Particulars</em> (2012 NYC Fringe Award for Overall Excellence in Performance), <em>H4,</em> and <em>Advance Man.</em> As a playwright his work includes <em>Savior</em> (Comic Book Theatre Festival), <em>The Magic of Mrs. Crowling</em> (published by Original Works) and many more. TV credits include <em>Law and Order: SVU</em>, <em>Boardwalk Empire</em>, and the next season of <em>Orange Is The New Black</em>.
[/one_fourth_last]

